          <p class="mb-0 mt-3">At FOSDEM 2020 we’re having the 1st edition of a Devroom completely dedicated to the BEAM (and all languages running on it). FOSDEM is an annual conference about free and open source software, attended by over 5000 developers and open-source enthusiasts from all over the world.</p>
          <a class="h5 mt-4 d-block" href="lonestar-elixir-2020">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
