        </div>
        <div class="py-4 pr-4">
          <h3><a class="text-dark font-weight-bold" href="#">Code BEAM SF 2020</a></h3>
          <h5 class="mb-0">February 1 @ 10:30:00 - February 1 @ 13:30:00</h5>
          <p class="mb-0 mt-3">Learn from 50+ cutting-edge talks and our in-depth training program, how BEAM languages are revolutionising areas like IoT, Blockchain, Fintech, Security, Machine Learning and more.</p>
          <a class="h5 mt-4 d-block" href="code-beam-sf-2020">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
